parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS modulator valve can cause the vehicle to swerve or lose control when the brakes are applied, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle swerves into another lane when the brakes are applied
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the ABS system makes a noise but fails to engage
the vehicle fails to stop or slows down unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle fails to stop or slows down unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose control or fail to stop, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ABS system makes a noise but fails to engage
the vehicle fails to stop or slows down unexpectedly
the brake pedal pulsates
the steering wheel shakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the master cylinder can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle fails to stop or slows down unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the folding rear seat anchors can cause the seat to become detached from the floor, leading to a loss of structural integrity and potentially causing injuries or accidents, especially in the event of sudden stops or crashes.
symptoms: The folding rear seat ripped from the floor when folded to an upright position
the bolts remained in the seat
the seat anchors rusted out and remained in the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden engine stalling can cause loss of power, loss of control, and increase the risk of accidents, especially on high-speed roads.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning
the vehicle loses power
the vehicle slows down or comes to a stop
the dashboard warning lights illuminate
the vehicle is difficult to restart.
